{"tid":1437761,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"邊個係機場搞嘉年華我屌邊個","createTime":"2019-08-09T15:21:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T15:28:03.000Z","uid":276124,"like":12,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ff048693aa591352ae746363c1be41ccca79ee80","tid":1437761,"uid":276124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:21:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Sorry做左標題黨</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n不過嘉年華咁又點<br />\n唱今天我就割席？<br />\n再咁割席落去我地好快輸<br />\n所以唔好比瘋狂割席嘅五毛帶風向好緊要<br />\n派膠又好 今天我又好 和理非又好 勇武又好<br />\n唔割席先有得贏<br />\n當年輸唔係輸係派膠 係互屌<br />\n和理非屌勇武暴力 勇武屌和理非今天我嘉年華<br />\n其實前日觀星都係膠都冇朋友<br />\n但係膠唔係問題<br />\n膠得黎令大家keep到團火<br />\n就膠得有作為<br />\n<br />\n記住我地嘅核心價值<br />\n兄弟爬山 各有各做<br />\n不割席 不督灰 不指責"},{"pid":"4bf07f779dd2a50caafabff9248335b92c625831","tid":1437761,"uid":293698,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:23:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e145948c55207a67b3d3dcd57a622d99e6cf6eb7","tid":1437761,"uid":276124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:23:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"99667adfc5e4e104ac3cf2fadc15769acdd1d305","tid":1437761,"uid":276124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:23:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"065711032888ba58b34c79af09ddbf6fc0e8dfb6","tid":1437761,"uid":22566,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:24:05.000Z","msg":"....唔知點回應你好 <br />\n但我覺得要嚴肅啲囉"},{"pid":"79b635a0c67e2f5077e41ab4d9ac504a90e51ab6","tid":1437761,"uid":276124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:24:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8179547284347125d6658c40cfbf89556e5b2c37","tid":1437761,"uid":276124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:24:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"45c9d92b0a7f84b2b497c2589ba44f3a2abe5ce5","tid":1437761,"uid":276124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:24:49.000Z","